p.k: Tirouli While playing with Pat and Hoodie Lola hears beautiful bird song. She looks in her dad’s ornithology book and finds out the bird is actually a parrot. Lola wants to take a photo of the bird and turn it into a star in her school. But the Guanos are jealo...
p.d: Despite his small size and playful attitude, Pat is the hero that flies to his friends' rescue while avoiding numerous obstacles that get in his way.
